<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="M" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Margaret" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Margaret,</orth> name of 1) Henry VI's queen: <bibl n="shak. 1h6 5.3.51" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A V, 3, 51</bibl>. 82 etc. <bibl n="shak. 2h6 1.1.4" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B I, 1, 4</bibl>. 16 etc. <bibl n="shak. 3h6 1.1.228" default="NO" valid="yes">H6C I, 1, 228</bibl> etc. <bibl n="shak. r3 1.2.93" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 I, 2, 93</bibl> etc. <cit><quote>--'s battle at Saint Albans,</quote> <bibl n="shak. r3 1.3.130" default="NO" valid="yes">I, 3, 130</bibl></cit>. 2) a waiting gentlewoman in <bibl n="shak. ado 2.2.13" default="NO" valid="yes">Ado II, 2, 13</bibl> etc.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>